snippet.title: POKEPIA ポケピア First Look Simulation Gameplay (iOS/Android)
snippet.description:
Hi guys, Welcome Back to Pokepia ポケピア! Pokepia is the simulation friendship game where you can do the summon gacha to collect new decorations for your home and costume, accessories for your character. You can visit other's home to water their plants so you level up your player rank. Pokepia is the new simulation game in iOS/Android. 🙏 please help to support this channel by subscribe, watch, like, comment and share. Thank you very much guys 🙏!

Check out this playlist for more Mobile iOS/Android game preview videos:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLv5rE5E2lvgRlnGH_Dt0zXgk_wtYWNb9v

We have our Discord Community, let's create a healthy environment with our gaming hobby & experience: https://discord.gg/ggXwEk3 Let's be friend here, chit-chat, and gaming!

Thank you for your support for this channel. You can subscribe this channel & Turn on bell notification:
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 
📍 Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/c/SCAWAKENINGshao?sub_confirmation=1
📍 Twitter: https://twitter.com/ShaoChunTheHero
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 
Thanks you very much

#shaochun #shao #ポケピア #pokepia #pokecolo
